1) In the query starting at QuickNetCore/Controllers/MaterialRequisitionController.cs:790, remove the three server-side let clauses (lines 802-806: let app / let AppStatus / let chkAppStatus). Keep let po/pq (FirstOrDefault scalars translate fine) and the joins/where unchanged. End the base query with the existing .ToList() on line 860 to materialize base rows (call it serverRows), projecting WITHOUT app/AppStatus/chkAppStatus.

